      },
      "contents": "<div class=\"markitup-box\">\n\t\t\tn主要还是看你研究什么<br/>\n比如你研究历史 冷战的话估计要懂一些俄语之类的<br/>\n<br/>\n不过英语基本上完全够用<br/>\n<br/>\n前提是有人做过之前类似的翻译工作\t\t</div>",
      "date": "2023-05-12",
      "agree_count": 3,
      "discussion_count": 0,
      "discussions": []
    },
    {
      "id": "654645",
      "is_folded": false,
      "answerer": {
        "username": "一Watcher一",
        "uid": "103381"
      },
      "contents": "<div class=\"markitup-box\">\n\t\t\t语言只是工具而已，要求会英语根本上是要求有阅读文献和国际范围内学术交流的能力。硬要求一个外在工具（英语）而不硬要求核心（教育背景和科研能力）简直买椟还珠。<br/>\n<br/>\n各国英语不好主要用母语搞研究的大有人在。\t\t</div>",
      "date": "2023-05-12",
      "agree_count": 3,
      "discussion_count": 0,
      "discussions": []
    },
    {
      "id": "654633",
      "is_folded": false,
      "answerer": {
        "username": "VyYxpU5oCezbWr",
        "uid": "111251"
      },
      "contents": "<div class=\"markitup-box\">\n\t\t\t題主談到algebraic geometry，個人想法是Alexandre G的寫作手法使得EGA、FGA以及其他一些書信(及那本自傳)過於難翻譯，其用詞富有『詩意』(一些數學家原話)，加上這些數量過大，也使得其難翻譯。<br/>\n<br/>\n此外，似乎多數人建議讀EGA原文，可能這種『傳統』使得鮮有人下手翻譯？\t\t</div>",
      "date": "2023-05-12",
      "agree_count": 0,
      "discussion_count": 0,
      "discussions": []
    },
    {
      "id": "654641",
      "is_folded": false,
      "answerer": {
        "username": "Olivert",
        "uid": "73427"
      },
      "contents": "<div class=\"markitup-box\">\n\t\t\t现在很多PhD program已经取消了对外语的要求，至少数学是这样。<br/>\nhttps://www.quora.com/To-get-a-PhD-in-mathematics-do-you-need-to-demonstrate-proficiency-in-one-of-Russian-German-or-French\t\t</div>",
      "date": "2023-05-12",
      "agree_count": 0,
      "discussion_count": 0,
      "discussions": []
    },
    {
      "id": "654643",
      "is_folded": false,
      "answerer": {
        "username": "rowlandheights",
        "uid": "108549"
      },
      "contents": "<div class=\"markitup-box\">\n\t\t\t交流不需要，研究看领域，如果该领域需要其他语言就需要\t\t</div>",
